  "title": "20 people observed a multicolor UFO for 1 hour in  Curitiba-PR [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/04/20-people-observed-a-multicolor-ufo-for-1-hour-in-curitiba-pr-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1oO",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 15th, 1994</strong>. Time: 20:05. Duration: 1 hour. In Curitiba, Paraná State, about 20 people spotted an unidentified flying object moving south. According to the witness that reported the sighting, the UFO was red and sometimes changed to yellow. The same witness was unable to estimate the size and shape of the object that emitted the lights. It was informed that there was filming of the sighting, but the video file was not made available.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.353. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Nova Terra, Estado do Paraná</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
